data.description: Your waterfront estate dream awaits! Nestled on .85 acres of pure natural beauty with over 220 feet of pristine shoreline on Star Lake, this property is a slice of paradise adjacent to the Pensacola Country Club and Perdido Bay, offering easy bay access. With a boat dock, 6000lbs lift, and jet port, it's a boater's dream come true. As you step onto this charming property, you'll be greeted by majestic mature oak trees and meticulously landscaped grounds that exude old southern charm. Enjoy serene moments on the back patio or take a dip in the enclosed heated gunite saltwater pool while you watch dolphins play and herons nest. Inside the 3400 square foot main house, you'll find 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, each room boasting incredible sunset views facing west. Hardwood, tile, and slate floors, along with elegant crown molding, enhance the beauty of every space. Cozy up to one of the three fireplaces on cooler evenings. The primary suite offers double vanities and a spacious walk-in closet. The property also includes a three-car garage with ample space, featuring an adjoining room that could serve as a guest room, pool room, man cave, or home office with a full bathroom. Additional features that make this home stand out include a backyard shed, three water heaters, two HVAC systems, a whole-home generator for peace of mind, an irrigation system, a soothing fountain, hurricane shutters, and so much more. Simply put, this house has it all! Don't miss your chance to experience the beauty, tranquility, and luxury of waterfront living. This is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Contact us today to schedule your private showing and make this exquisite waterfront estate yours!
